abstract: It may be Election Day, but the outcome won't end uncertainty for Wall Street. | Morgan Stanley is betting that Colm Kelleher has what it takes to revive its securities unit. | Mark E. Tucker, chief executive and president of the AIA Group, is joining Goldman Sachs's board.

headline.main: The Big Day, but More Uncertainty to Come
